📘 Student Score Prediction using Linear Regression

## 🔍 Project Goal
To predict a student's exam score based on the number of hours studied using simple linear regression.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Python 🐍
- Pandas
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn

---

## 📊 Dataset
A small dataset with two columns:
- Hours (No. of study hours)
- Scores (Marks obtained)

---

## 🔁 Steps Involved

1. Load and understand the data
2. Visualize the relationship between study hours and scores
3. Prepare data and split into training & testing sets
4. Train a Linear Regression model
5. Predict and evaluate the model using MAE
6. Visualize Actual vs Predicted scores
